role_dependencies: Installs Java on nearly any OS
role_description: An Ansible role that installs wkhtmltopdf (a command line tool to render HTML into PDF and various image formats) on nearly any platform
role_description_full_overview: [wkhtmltopdf](https://github.com/wkhtmltopdf/wkhtmltopdf) is a command line tool to render HTML into PDF and various image formats using the QT Webkit rendering engine.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that installs wkhtmltopdf (a command line tool to render HTML into PDF and various image formats) on nearly any platform.
